    AbstractTreeForTreeLayout<TreeNode>

    Used to configure the tree layout algorithm.

    Possible alignments of a node within a level (centered, towards or away from root)
    Configuration.Location
    Identifies the sides of a rectangle (top, left, ...)
    Constants
    Class with multiple "constants", they are not static due to the possibility of being accessed by multiple Threads, and because of that an object of type Constants will be passed around when creating a city, so only after reset will changes be applied(Intended use)

    A set of methods to support some sort of "Design by Contract" programming.
